messageBody:
Hello Everyone:

 

I have created two short polls for the purpose of getting some idea of how our members use QS and how long they have been using it.  I would encourage you to go to the Yahoo site and answer the polls as I believe it will be quite interesting to see how we are using QS in our daily lives.  Thanks.

 

Paige Gabhart
